reviewText:
This video gets 4 stars due to its length (1/2 hour) and current selling price. Songs and artists featured are as follows:

Everybody Rock Now-Garbo Talks, Bad Seamstress Blues/Fallin' Apart At The Seams-Cinderella, 17 Crash-L.A. Guns, Gung Ho-Anthrax, The Last Mile-Cinderella, Driving On Holy Gasoline-Zodiac Mindwarp, Faster Than The Speed Of Light-Yngwie Malmsteen.
